name: I Wanna Say Sasameku
description:
A game made for the I Wanna Tourney event, It is an adventure game of ~60 difficulty.

Additions from the tourney version include:

  • Warp Room
  • EX Stage
  • Slightly Nerfed Final Boss
  • Comedy
